skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: purple sky
des: Play an interesting game of quiz with Alexa on your knowledge of Prince. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz. You will be quizzed on how deep and obscure your knowledge is of Prince and his music. This quiz will test and enlighten the "I like Purple Rain" fan as well as the True Funk Soldiers.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
